    "description": "Last souls is a 2D side-scrolling Metroidvania soulslike game.<br>The player controls a mysterious caped character and explores a labyrinthine, dark and cold world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792360/extras/10fc72e46a6cec5634d2bac3cc63b15f.poster.avif?t=1698351055\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792360/extras/10fc72e46a6cec5634d2bac3cc63b15f.webm?t=1698351055\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792360/extras/10fc72e46a6cec5634d2bac3cc63b15f.mp4?t=1698351055\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The world of Last souls is divided into 7 regions.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>cave</li><li>poisonous forest</li><li>abandoned mine</li><li>burning cavern</li><li>bottomless pit</li><li>misty lake</li><li>frozen city</li><li>peak of the gods</li></ul><br>Each region has a boss who give an ability.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792360/extras/5e348de52aa921a3afc64ce0436ce3e1.poster.avif?t=1698351055\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792360/extras/5e348de52aa921a3afc64ce0436ce3e1.webm?t=1698351055\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792360/extras/5e348de52aa921a3afc64ce0436ce3e1.mp4?t=1698351055\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>More than 30 weapons divided into 5 classes.<br>Many different spells and &quot;talisements&quot; that influence the gameplay.<br>Various skills and a crafting system of consumables.<br><br>I present you my first game &quot;Last Souls&quot;, student in computer science, I decided to start creating video games.<br>The game is not finished yet, but I'm working on it 100%.<br>I hope you will like it :]",
